profile_summary:
Amjad C P is a highly skilled web application pentester, mentor, and DevOps expert with a strong background in Python, JavaScript, and TypeScript. With a notable presence on GitHub, Amjad has built a professional network of 44 followers, demonstrating his influence and reputation within the developer community. His extensive portfolio of 74 public repositories showcases his active involvement in development and commitment to delivering high-quality solutions. As a seasoned web-app pentester, Amjad has developed a unique ability to identify vulnerabilities and implement robust security measures, ensuring the integrity and reliability of web applications.

With a focus on innovation and collaboration, Amjad excels in mentoring and guiding junior developers, sharing his expertise and best practices to help them grow and succeed. His expertise in DevOps enables him to bridge the gap between development and operations, ensuring seamless deployment and optimal performance of web applications. By leveraging his technical skills and industry knowledge, Amjad delivers cutting-edge solutions that meet the evolving needs of the digital landscape. With his strong technical foundation, professional achievements, and passion for mentoring, Amjad C P is a trusted and reliable partner for businesses and individuals seeking expert web application development, security, and DevOps services.
